<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>My god do I feel stupid.  He has jumped me 4 times on my way to hunt boots in Unrest (I was 31-35 at the time).  Three of those times (I think) I was with a cleric of my level.  What did I do?  I ran...figured not worth it, he's beating on me pretty good I'll just zone.  I am kicking myself hard.  <BR>
